msp430 support is limited at this time:

use crossdev -t msp430 to build binutils 
for now i use  


wget ftp://ftp.informatik.rwth-aachen.de/pub/gnu/gcc/gcc-3.3.6/gcc-core-3.3.6.tar.bz2
wget ftp://ftp.cs.univ-paris8.fr/mirrors/ftp.gnu.org/gnu/binutils/binutils-2.17.tar.bz2
### checkout cvs from msp430.sf.net


tar jxf binutils*
cd binutils*
./configure --target=msp430 --prefix=/opt/msp_2007_03_04
make 
make install 
cd ../


tar jxf gcc-core-3.3.6.tar.bz2 
cd gcc-core-3.3.6 
# version mismatch intended ...  
cp -r ~/cvstrees/mspgcc/gcc/gcc-3.4/* .
./configure --target=msp430 --prefix=/opt/msp_2007_03_04
make 
make install 


this builds a msp430 compiler + basic tools in /opt/msp_2007_03_04



